Speech-to-Text Using Azure Speech Services

üó£Ô∏è Overview
Azure Speech Services convert spoken audio into text, enabling voice-controlled applications and transcription.

Program:
import azure.cognitiveservices.speech as speechsdk

speech_key = "9VZbnCZ0CCm4xYTKTslmLzPKe588visu9MWrqofpGRSphcgRDhchJQQJ99BKACGhslBXJ3w3AAAYACOGIxSE"
service_region = "centralindia"

speech_config = speechsdk.SpeechConfig(subscription=speech_key, region=service_region)
audio_config = speechsdk.audio.AudioConfig(filename="sample.wav")
speech_recognizer = speechsdk.SpeechRecognizer(speech_config=speech_config, audio_config=audio_config)

result = speech_recognizer.recognize_once()
print("Recognized text:", result.text)
